<normalizedToken originalValue="µm">µm</normalizedToken>
thick, outer layer 25-45 
<normalizedToken originalValue="µm">µm</normalizedToken>
thick, of textura globulosa to textura angularis; inner layer 7-25 
<normalizedToken originalValue="µm">µm</normalizedToken>
thick, of textura prismatica. Asci unitunicate, clavate, 8-spored, 93-130 
